data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled in the small town of Tom Bean, Texas. This residence features three bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family. The master bedroom is a peaceful retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom, ensuring privacy and convenience. The dining area is perfect for hosting meals and enjoying the view of the backyard. The heart of this home is its big, beautiful backyard, adorned with mature trees that provide shade and privacy. Imagine spending lazy afternoons or hosting gatherings in this serene outdoor spot. Located in the town of Tom Bean, you'll enjoy a friendly community atmosphere.
